{"tid":371300,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"其實女仔只係想搵到一個愛佢既人","createTime":"2017-08-23T15:11:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-23T18:11:59.000Z","uid":134054,"like":5,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"35cd4df019104e242827b3b882b21cdf295fbd23","tid":371300,"uid":134054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T15:11:29.000Z","msg":"戀愛好美好 : <br />\n開始一段關係好易 但點樣維持先係最難 <br />\n每段分手總係有某d原因先會咁<br />\n如果多d講出嚟 互相遷就 互相支持 只要愛對方幾辛苦都可以捱過去 <br />\n我諗無一個問題可以纏住你成世<br />\n竟然可以解決到咁就可以一齊既話點解唔解決呢？ <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現實係:<br />\n1.因為對方根本唔鐘意你<br />\n2.個d問題佢覺得太煩唔想解決<br />\n3.想飛你好耐 頂你唔順"},{"pid":"f0a7150693d81e92c75cd5baf02d9a2dc2c4e909","tid":371300,"uid":12980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T15:17:02.000Z","msg":"個男仔肯改又點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd8c545a3863f3a78467d29ec2fba9025de67ee6","tid":371300,"uid":5921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T15:23:20.000Z","msg":"愛你既你唔愛"},{"pid":"63abc7e73fcdd1c80d983fda8d5febbf1d1bdc07","tid":371300,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T15:23:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>愛你既你唔愛</blockquote>"},{"pid":"75f4fad58bd680ed269385f70d0bd9121c4c3e99","tid":371300,"uid":68598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T15:58:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>愛你既你唔愛</blockquote></blockquote>"},{"pid":"643a7dd5813d752f97a2bae4b3b610a28b2348dc","tid":371300,"uid":68589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T16:00:52.000Z","msg":"如果係因為2仲有無方法救"},{"pid":"f8df58dc34301c6796256cb1d8a5f6b7217a2c83","tid":371300,"uid":134054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T18:11:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果係因為2仲有無方法救</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n連解決既耐性都無 點講一生一世 / 愛 <br />\n所以最後都係分手收場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}